{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "START",
      "type": "start",
      "text": "Good evening. Let’s take a moment to reflect on your day.",
      "target": "A1_OPEN"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_OPEN",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "How would you describe your day overall?",
      "options": [
        "Productive",
        "Challenging",
        "Mixed",
        "Frustrating"
      ],
      "target": "A1_DECISION"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_DECISION",
      "type": "decision",
      "rules": [
        {
          "condition": "answer=Productive|Mixed",
          "target": "A1_Q_HIGH"
        },
        {
          "condition": "answer=Challenging|Frustrating",
          "target": "A1_Q_LOW"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_Q_HIGH",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "What contributed most to things going well today?",
      "options": [
        "I planned and executed well",
        "I adapted quickly",
        "My team supported me",
        "It worked out by chance"
      ],
      "signal_map": {
        "I planned and executed well": "axis1:internal",
        "I adapted quickly": "axis1:internal",
        "My team supported me": "axis1:external",
        "It worked out by chance": "axis1:external"
      },
      "target": "A1_SIGNAL_DECISION"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_Q_LOW",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When things didn’t go as expected, how did you respond?",
      "options": [
        "I focused on what I could control",
        "I waited for help",
        "I felt stuck",
        "I continued without adjusting my approach"
      ],
      "signal_map": {
        "I focused on what I could control": "axis1:internal",
        "I waited for help": "axis1:external",
        "I felt stuck": "axis1:external",
        "I continued without adjusting my approach": "axis1:internal"
      },
      "target": "A1_Q_EXTRA"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_Q_EXTRA",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When facing difficulty, what guided your decision most?",
      "options": [
        "My own judgment",
        "Advice from others",
        "Circumstances",
        "I wasn’t sure what to do"
      ],
      "signal_map": {
        "My own judgment": "axis1:internal",
        "Advice from others": "axis1:external",
        "Circumstances": "axis1:external",
        "I wasn’t sure what to do": "axis1:external"
      },
      "target": "A1_SIGNAL_DECISION"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_SIGNAL_DECISION",
      "type": "decision",
      "rules": [
        {
          "condition": "axis1.internal >= axis1.external",
          "target": "A1_REFLECT_INTERNAL"
        },
        {
          "condition": "axis1.external > axis1.internal",
          "target": "A1_REFLECT_EXTERNAL"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_REFLECT_INTERNAL",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You described your day as '{A1_OPEN.answer}'. You recognized your role in how the day unfolded. Even small actions shaped outcomes — that’s agency.",
      "target": "BRIDGE_1_2"
    },
    {
      "id": "A1_REFLECT_EXTERNAL",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You described your day as '{A1_OPEN.answer}'. It may have felt like things were out of your control today. Still, even in difficult moments, small choices exist. Noticing them is where control begins.",
      "target": "BRIDGE_1_2"
    },
    {
      "id": "BRIDGE_1_2",
      "type": "bridge",
      "text": "Now that you’ve looked at how you handled your day, let’s shift focus to what you contributed.",
      "target": "A2_OPEN"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_OPEN",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Which best describes your role in interactions today?",
      "options": [
        "I helped others beyond my role",
        "I did what was expected of me",
        "I expected more support than I received",
        "I felt others weren’t doing enough"
      ],
      "signal_map": {
        "I helped others beyond my role": "axis2:contribution",
        "I did what was expected of me": "axis2:neutral",
        "I expected more support than I received": "axis2:entitlement",
        "I felt others weren’t doing enough": "axis2:entitlement"
      },
      "target": "A2_Q1"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_Q1",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Think of one moment today. What was your focus in that moment?",
      "options": [
        "Helping someone succeed",
        "Finishing my own task efficiently",
        "Making sure my effort was recognized",
        "Noticing where others fell short"
      ],
      "signal_map": {
        "Helping someone succeed": "axis2:contribution",
        "Finishing my own task efficiently": "axis2:neutral",
        "Making sure my effort was recognized": "axis2:entitlement",
        "Noticing where others fell short": "axis2:entitlement"
      },
      "target": "A2_SIGNAL_DECISION"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_SIGNAL_DECISION",
      "type": "decision",
      "rules": [
        {
          "condition": "axis2.contribution > axis2.entitlement",
          "target": "A2_REFLECT_CONTRIB"
        },
        {
          "condition": "axis2.entitlement >= axis2.contribution",
          "target": "A2_REFLECT_ENTITLE"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_REFLECT_CONTRIB",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "You spent energy contributing and supporting outcomes beyond just your own tasks. That kind of focus tends to create momentum—not just for you, but for the people around you.",
      "target": "BRIDGE_2_3"
    },
    {
      "id": "A2_REFLECT_ENTITLE",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "There were moments where your attention leaned toward what wasn’t given or what others didn’t do. That’s natural. Shifting even a small part of that attention toward what you can contribute often changes how those situations unfold.",
      "target": "BRIDGE_2_3"
    },
    {
      "id": "BRIDGE_2_3",
      "type": "bridge",
      "text": "Now let’s widen the lens—beyond just your role—to the impact of your actions.",
      "target": "A3_OPEN"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_OPEN",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "When you think about today, who comes to mind most?",
      "options": [
        "Just myself and my workload",
        "My immediate tasks and deadlines",
        "My team and shared outcomes",
        "People I impacted (customers/colleagues)"
      ],
      "signal_map": {
        "Just myself and my workload": "axis3:self",
        "My immediate tasks and deadlines": "axis3:self",
        "My team and shared outcomes": "axis3:others",
        "People I impacted (customers/colleagues)": "axis3:others"
      },
      "target": "A3_Q1"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_Q1",
      "type": "question",
      "text": "Which statement best reflects your impact today?",
      "options": [
        "I supported someone’s progress",
        "I focused mainly on completing my own work",
        "My actions caused delays or confusion",
        "I improved someone’s experience or outcome"
      ],
      "signal_map": {
        "I supported someone’s progress": "axis3:others",
        "I focused mainly on completing my own work": "axis3:self",
        "My actions caused delays or confusion": "axis3:self",
        "I improved someone’s experience or outcome": "axis3:others"
      },
      "target": "A3_SIGNAL_DECISION"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_SIGNAL_DECISION",
      "type": "decision",
      "rules": [
        {
          "condition": "axis3.others > axis3.self",
          "target": "A3_REFLECT_OTHERS"
        },
        {
          "condition": "axis3.self >= axis3.others",
          "target": "A3_REFLECT_SELF"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_REFLECT_OTHERS",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "Your attention extended beyond your own tasks. You considered how your actions affected others—and that’s where meaningful impact tends to grow.",
      "target": "SUMMARY"
    },
    {
      "id": "A3_REFLECT_SELF",
      "type": "reflection",
      "text": "Most of your focus stayed on your own work today. That’s understandable. Even small shifts toward considering others can change both outcomes and how the day feels.",
      "target": "SUMMARY"
    },
    {
      "id": "SUMMARY",
      "type": "summary",
      "text": "Today you reflected on how you handled situations, what you contributed, and how your actions affected others. These patterns aren’t fixed—they can shift with small, intentional changes.",
      "target": "END"
    },
    {
      "id": "END",
      "type": "end",
      "text": "That’s it for today. See you tomorrow."
    }
  ]
}
